546
00:24:16,958 --> 00:24:18,750
Taku... Those words.

547
00:24:21,333 --> 00:24:22,250
Wow.

548
00:24:23,958 --> 00:24:25,333
First pick out a color

549
00:24:25,416 --> 00:24:28,041
